# MemoryNode API — minimal local variables (Mode 3)
#
# Wrangler reads secrets from `apps/api/.dev.vars`, not from dotenv files.
# Copy each key/value you need into `.dev.vars` (start from `.dev.vars.template`).
#
# --- Required for a working local API (database-backed) ---
# SUPABASE_URL=
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=
# SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=          # if you use dashboard flows against local API
# SUPABASE_JWT_SECRET=        # if you use dashboard flows
# API_KEY_SALT=
# MASTER_ADMIN_TOKEN=
#
# --- Recommended for cheap local iteration ---
# SUPABASE_MODE=dev
# EMBEDDINGS_MODE=stub        # no OpenAI spend; deterministic embeddings
# ENVIRONMENT=dev
#
# Full operator list: see `.env.advanced.example` and `docs/self-host/LOCAL_DEV.md`.
